    {
      "id": "edqeNeRq2F-zoaUi5z_25",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3123.7286660405794,
      "y": 4541.477277256439,
      "width": 318.43975830078125,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "BE72cmouS9J60Py141tY8",
        "Mvzk5LPzAjYbIjt8uTTCE",
        "dbvjxZWhsflRUzENFGwze",
        "Ztw7NzeA3kb3fcRAmbTej",
        "IpAYJ0OK8OqgXtxotb_7S"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHwY",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1252647468,
      "version": 1078,
      "versionNonce": 1875964943,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775391951880,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "CMS：写屏障 + 增量更新\nG1，Shenandoah：写屏障 + SATB \nZGC：读屏障",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CMS：写屏障 + 增量更新\nG1，Shenandoah：写屏障 + SATB \nZGC：读屏障",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "nmh5vv_yHAmfmAOWFtcMY",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3117.7285846603704,
      "y": 4666.699485915295,
      "width": 1215.3199462890625,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "BE72cmouS9J60Py141tY8",
        "Mvzk5LPzAjYbIjt8uTTCE",
        "dbvjxZWhsflRUzENFGwze",
        "Ztw7NzeA3kb3fcRAmbTej",
        "IpAYJ0OK8OqgXtxotb_7S"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHwZ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1622293908,
      "version": 1141,
      "versionNonce": 1423284783,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775391951881,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "为什么G1用SATB？CMS用增量更新？\n我的理解：SATB相对增量更新效率会高(当然SATB可能造成更多的浮动垃圾)，因为不需要在重新标记阶段再次深度扫描被删除引用对象，\n而CMS对增量引用的根对象会做深度扫描，G1因为很多对象都位于不同的region，CMS就一块老年代区域，重新深度扫描对象的话G1的\n代价会比CMS高，所以G1选择SATB不深度扫描对象，只是简单标记，等到下一轮GC再深度扫描。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "为什么G1用SATB？CMS用增量更新？\n我的理解：SATB相对增量更新效率会高(当然SATB可能造成更多的浮动垃圾)，因为不需要在重新标记阶段再次深度扫描被删除引用对象，\n而CMS对增量引用的根对象会做深度扫描，G1因为很多对象都位于不同的region，CMS就一块老年代区域，重新深度扫描对象的话G1的\n代价会比CMS高，所以G1选择SATB不深度扫描对象，只是简单标记，等到下一轮GC再深度扫描。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "IHDEi-vpeH5h4RYaoTYxV",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": -3143.728767765838,
      "y": 4520.588625726488,
      "width": 1266.1114807128906,
      "height": 280,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
