    },
    {
      "id": "TLl2WCwepyeYmGAlXmbRZ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3127.2691691640302,
      "y": 4193.276052096757,
      "width": 321.8799743652344,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dotted",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "DbRYmj3wQYD_tt59tgieS",
        "BE72cmouS9J60Py141tY8",
        "Mvzk5LPzAjYbIjt8uTTCE",
        "dbvjxZWhsflRUzENFGwze",
        "Ztw7NzeA3kb3fcRAmbTej",
        "IpAYJ0OK8OqgXtxotb_7S"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHwb",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 664056236,
      "version": 903,
      "versionNonce": 1158290031,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775391951881,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "什么场景适合使用G1\n1. 50%以上的堆被存活对象占用\n2. 对象分配和晋升的速度变化非常大\n3. 垃圾回收时间特别长，超过1秒\n4. 8GB以上的堆内存(建议值)\n5. 停顿时间是500ms以内",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "什么场景适合使用G1\n1. 50%以上的堆被存活对象占用\n2. 对象分配和晋升的速度变化非常大\n3. 垃圾回收时间特别长，超过1秒\n4. 8GB以上的堆内存(建议值)\n5. 停顿时间是500ms以内",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "W_8NGQ96gpRmmjl9ep0_b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -3121.468845677702,
      "y": 4366.609436292718,
      "width": 988.399658203125,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "DbRYmj3wQYD_tt59tgieS",
        "BE72cmouS9J60Py141tY8",
        "Mvzk5LPzAjYbIjt8uTTCE",
        "dbvjxZWhsflRUzENFGwze",
        "Ztw7NzeA3kb3fcRAmbTej",
        "IpAYJ0OK8OqgXtxotb_7S"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cHwc",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 668633876,
      "version": 1118,
      "versionNonce": 1222309007,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775391951881,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "示例：\n每秒几十万并发Kafka：\n伊甸区增长30-40G需要1分钟，回收30-40G需要几秒，导致每几秒卡顿做一次fullgc；\n设置-XX:MaxGCPauseMills 为50ms，使50ms回收3-4G内存；50ms卡顿范围内一边回收垃圾一边处理用户线程\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "示例：\n每秒几十万并发Kafka：\n伊甸区增长30-40G需要1分钟，回收30-40G需要几秒，导致每几秒卡顿做一次fullgc；\n设置-XX:MaxGCPauseMills 为50ms，使50ms回收3-4G内存；50ms卡顿范围内一边回收垃圾一边处理用户线程\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
